dc_title_s: Morris County, New Jersey highways 1967 map 3
dc_description_s: Base map of Morris County. Sheet three of a six sheet map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. Series includes 35 insets of major road junctures. State highways as of Dec. 31, 1967. Culture, county roads and municipal streets are as of 1940.
